'''Free-traders''' were independent, small-time [[Merchant/Legends|merchants]]. They traveled [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] as they wished, trading commodities by buying and selling goods, and were always on the lookout for a good deal. A free-trader considered their [[Starship/Legends|starship]] to be their home and transport.<ref name="RPG" />

As the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] tightened its rule on the galaxy, free-traders found themselves squeezed and faced with more restrictions as more and more tradeable goods became illegal. Some free-traders found themselves borrowing money from [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lords]] to remain operational, or took to [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggling]] illegal cargos.<ref name="RPG" />

